I’m counting on you right now

My situation is in your hands, Peter.
I’m writing today to give you an update and to make a humble plea. Look – this is from the bottom of my heart, so please read this message to the end.
My team and I put together a historic win in 2021 to help flip all three of Virginia’s highest offices red. Ever since becoming Lt. Governor, I’ve been logging big wins for my friends, neighbors, and every fellow Virginian. Now, I’m running for Governor so we can continue to keep up the amazing work we’ve been doing here in the Commonwealth and make history again.
**But right now I have a few SERIOUS challenges:**
**__I was legally barred from accepting even a dime in support of my campaign while I was in the Virginia legislative session. But my Democrat opponent, Abigail Spanberger, has been fundraising BIG TIME while I’ve been working hard in our capital. Seriously, a far-Left group injected $500K into Abigail Spanberger’s campaign coffers and there wasn’t a thing I could do in response!__**
Now Spanberger has an ENORMOUS fundraising advantage, Peter. Polls show this race is tied, but Spanberger has a serious cash advantage. If we don’t make up the difference, our conservative mission will be cut short.
